.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:06:52.000Z","msg":"戰狼出發緊去救佢，一定無事<br />\n唔好忘記你背後有強大祖國。<br />\n厲害了，我的國！"},{"pid":"0804f80ebfe8fc427854872558f8a71432f6bca9","tid":1042780,"uid":31475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d379df413673c45ca1d932458f253d7ae4b6bd4c","tid":1042780,"uid":37699,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T21:32:08.000Z","msg":"係「批准引渡聆訊」。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大司法部周五下午宣布，批准華為副董事長孟晚舟引渡聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n司法部周五批准就引渡孟晚舟進行法庭聆訊，法官可聽取有關是否批准美國引渡孟晚舟到美國受審判的論點，該案件於下周三會返回卑詩省最高法院出席聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大司法部的聲明指出，有足夠證據讓法院決定是否符合兩國之間的引渡協議，強調聆訊並不是要裁定孟晚舟是否有罪。<br />\n<br />\n法庭有引導判決後，司法部長 David Lametti 最終必須決定孟是否被引渡。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:17:58.000Z","msg":"連登仔柒晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2eb220cd777f595d97398192517eb13519f492a","tid":1042780,"uid":16830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"841c62e913745f0d007c1dab55394557cad71ce7","tid":1042780,"uid":190431,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"9df302b40f1dcc533f2afc3831a7aabd07e0d88c","tid":1042780,"uid":131423,"like":148,"dislike":0,"score":148,"quote":{"pid":"a3e63778a6293d049b19ea46210431f38e33f930","tid":1042780,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T19:15:04.000Z","msg":"source?"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T19:19:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2019/03/01/canadian-government-allows-extradition-of-huawei-cfo-to-the-us.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2019%2F03%2F01%2Fcanadian-government-allows-extradition-of-huawei-cfo-to-the-us.html&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7C7tFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=5877215c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2019/03/01/canadian-government-allows-extradition-of-huawei-cfo-to-the-us.html</a><br />\n出哂新聞，睇黎堅了<br />\n佢會唔會即刻衝入中國大使館<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif